Technologies: Type O3, Laravel, Symphony, WordPress, PHP, JavaScript, CSS

Preference for developers with a mix of practical experience in coding and theoretical knowledge. Practical problem-solving and the ability to work with existing codebases are crucial.

Following the interview, Marcus has decided to begin working with Dmitry for full time.
